{"tid":173383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好為啲唔識得珍惜嘅人去爭取任何嘢","createTime":"2017-03-26T07:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T11:11:19.000Z","uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"933232a53fa21d3d061ced0b854b6c6a2efa1e37","tid":173383,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T07:33:46.000Z","msg":"要爭取之前，首要佢地都想去珍惜，想去爭取。唯一做到就係將佢地有嘅都全部攞走。<br />\n要佢地識爭取民主要首先令佢地一啲民主都無，選乜都選唔到。要被支配到窒息時人先會想自由。所以香港依家需要係大家加強大陸嘅糟塌。當香港俾大陸搞到一文不值，香港人無哂價值無哂尊嚴時，或者嗰時佢地先會肯企出黎去爭取"},{"pid":"9964ee9b5255aeab4ad81e7fefb8f344f11bad6f","tid":173383,"uid":62337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"咁有決心爭取民主點解唔自己爭取上游地位？大家想透過民主得到點樣既未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1729483b123ba87be0d102871e1bfbef93afd86","tid":173383,"uid":8589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:25:37.000Z","msg":"你估我想架 係我犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73453db3a6143b2a8cd2e27fd32f6670e76eb741","tid":173383,"uid":8589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"我希望有一日可以打動佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8f0acc8164908c5193db42e1acca5c97de073e","tid":173383,"uid":74933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T11:11:19.000Z","msg":"港豬會習慣<br />\n然後問你 宜家生活咪好地地 點解要搞咁多野？"}]}